Techniques | quadrant: top-right
  Continuous Deployment | ring: Adopt, trend: stable
    We've fully adopted **CD** across all services.
    Reduces release risk significantly.
  Infrastructure as Code | ring: Adopt, trend: stable
    All infrastructure managed via Terraform modules.
  Micro Frontends | ring: Trial, trend: up
    Exploring for the customer portal.
  Design Systems | ring: Adopt, trend: new
    Launched our shared component library.

Tools | quadrant: top-left
  GitHub Copilot | ring: Trial, trend: new
    Early results show 15-20% productivity gains.
  Vite | ring: Adopt, trend: up
    Default build tool for all new projects.
  Webpack | ring: Hold, trend: down
    Migrating remaining projects to Vite.
  Playwright | ring: Adopt, trend: stable
    Standard E2E testing framework.

Platforms | quadrant: bottom-left
  Kubernetes | ring: Adopt, trend: stable
    Primary orchestration platform.
  Cloudflare Workers | ring: Trial, trend: up
    Testing for edge API layer.
  Serverless | ring: Trial, trend: stable
    Used selectively for event processing.

Languages & Frameworks | quadrant: bottom-right
  TypeScript | ring: Adopt, trend: stable
    Standard language for all new services.
  Rust | ring: Assess, trend: new
